{"tid":2276443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真求教] 外國籍人喺香港加入中国籍有乜好","createTime":"2020-11-07T23:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T00:26:53.000Z","uid":271714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b884551745b19647a3ac3678e58f479519103d","tid":2276443,"uid":271714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T23:52:20.000Z","msg":"老婆泰國人，喺香港住同做野都幾年，就拎到永久居民，個女就雙重國籍，我就火車頭、BNO，佢覺得去歐洲英國旅行好煩，得佢要搞簽證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之但係除左本火車頭之外，又唔覺得喺香港入左籍會同而家有乜唔同，仲未諗掂值唔值搞咁多野，有無巴打分享下喺香港係乜國籍有幾大影響？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713f764d980e83ed8e645435499f6fe8aebfb2c1","tid":2276443,"uid":264158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T00:25:34.000Z","msg":"搬去英國拎英籍咪唔駛煩囉"},{"pid":"f5e9eb3bafcf1966d54441db517e46219661851c","tid":2276443,"uid":102997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T00:26:53.000Z","msg":"「入中國藉」對你嚟講仲有討論空間嘅話<br />\n<br />\n快啲入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}